---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Base
  title="Car Rental Business Bay Dubai 2026 — From AED 35/day"
  description="Compare car rentals in Business Bay Dubai. Corporate and personal rentals. Economy from AED 35/day with delivery to your office or residence."
>
<div class="bg-navy text-white py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="text-sm text-blue-300 mb-2">📍 Business Bay</div>
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-3">Car Rental Business Bay — From AED 35/day</h1>
  <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Compare car rental companies in Business Bay. Delivery to your office tower or residence. Corporate rates available.</p>
  <a href="/get-quotes?ref=business-bay" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black hover:bg-yellow-300 transition-colors inline-block">Get Business Bay Car Rental Quotes →</a>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow p-4 mb-10">
    <iframe src="https://www.discovercars.com/engine/rent-a-car/iframe?a_aid=YOUR_AFFILIATE_ID&location=Business+Bay+Dubai&lang=en&curr=AED" width="100%" height="420" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="Business Bay Car Rental — Compare Prices"></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-navy">Car Rental in Business Bay</h2>
    <p>Business Bay is Dubai's commercial CBD with over 240 towers housing offices, residences, and hotels. Car rental companies deliver directly to tower lobbies and basement parking, making it one of the most convenient areas for pickup.</p>
    <p>Business Bay is adjacent to Downtown Dubai and connected to DIFC and Sheikh Zayed Road. Residents and corporate visitors frequently rent monthly at AED 900–1,200/month for economy cars — significantly cheaper than taxi commuting.</p>
    <p>Corporate fleet rates are available for companies needing 3+ vehicles. Monthly contracts include insurance, maintenance, and replacement vehicles.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-8 text-center">
    <a href="/car-rentals" class="text-brand font-semibold hover:underline">← Back to all car rental areas</a>
  </div>
</div>
</Base>
